  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7595042">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7595042/" class="title-link">假设与反思</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7595042"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/simaxuan/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u14635421-343.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/simaxuan/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">王小刀</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-09-09"
      class="main-meta">2015-09-09 10:16:47</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7595042_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  漫长的人类社会发展史，同时也是一部战争史，要先从浩繁的战争史中遴选出20场改变人类历史发展轨迹的战争，绝非易事。  作者从公元前490年的马拉松战役开始，一直叙说到了2003年的巴格达战争。这精挑细选的20场战争，从社会文明、上层建筑、经济基础等方方面面，影响着五大洲的...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7595042_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7595042_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评1篇
                </a>
            </p>
